          img.header__icon(src='./images/avatar.png', alt='')
      li.header__item
        a(href='#') LINKS
      li.header__item
        a(href='#') CONTACTS
  section.hero
    h1.hero__title
      | Motivation Is The First Step To
      span.hero_highlight Success
    ul.hero__icons
      li.hero__icon
        img(src='./images/twitter.svg', alt='')
      li.hero__icon
        img(src='./images/be.svg', alt='')
      li.hero__icon
        img(src='./images/insta.svg', alt='')
  section.works
    h1.works__title WORKS
    ul.works__items
      li.works__item
        .works__caption
          ul.tags
            li.tags__item Featured
          h2.works__label Motivation Is The First Step To Success
      li.works__item
        .works__caption
          h2.works__label How Great Is The Strength Of Your Belief
      li.works__item
        .works__caption
          h2.works__label Benjamin Franklin S Method Of Habit Formation
      li.works__item
        .works__caption
          ul.tags
            li.tags__item Featured
          h2.works__label Increasing Prosperity With Positive Thinking
  section.about
    h1.works__title ABOUT
    ul.about__items
      li.about__item
        h2.works__label UX/UI
        p.about__caption
          | Of course, motivation really isn’t simple at all. That is why there is multi-billion industry
          | focused on self-help books, tapes, seminars, camps, and coaches.
      li.about__item
        h2.works__label Motion
        p.about__caption
          | As humans, we have progressed in so many ways, but we have lost touch with our bodies, nature,
          | and the power of prayer. There seems to be a spiritual renaissance, of sorts, going on in the
          | “new age” movement.
      li.about__item
        h2.works__label Branding
        p.about__caption
          | If at anytime, you notice that a friend of yours is getting demotivated about life, try to
          | inspire him/her as much as you can. Even if you are physically away from your friend you can
          | send him inspirational ecards and tell him to download motivational screensavers and
          | wallpapers. So motivate everyone who needs the boost.
      li.about__item
        h2.works__label Development
        p.about__caption
          | Personally, the importance does not lie in what religion you are; however, a lack of religion
          | does seem to run parallel with depression. This is classified as spiritual illness, which will
          | have a negative effect on you mentally, physically, or totally.
    ul.about__logos
      li.about__logo
        img.about__logo-img(src='./images/google.svg', alt='')
      li.about__logo
        img.about__logo-img(src='./images/airbnb.svg', alt='')
      li.about__logo
        img.about__logo-img(src='./images/dropbox.svg', alt='')
